                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t17230828-8-defend63 t17230828-8-deflabel47"></join>, got up earlier than he usually did, and went out, and he saw him no more till the Tuesday Night, when he was taken up at Billingsgate by a Constable: That he own'd he had taken 5 l. 15 s. out of his Master's Drawer, and that he had paid the Fees of one of his Acquaintance, one Mason, and spent about 3 1. in Cloaths, clothing him from Head to Foot. Two other Evidences depos'd, They heard him own this before Sir 
